Subject: drm/exynos: Drop useless check from exynos_drm_{suspend,resume}
Git-commit: eebdc3b49abbfc7ab574eaddebfec64df27a5cf4
Patch-mainline: v4.19-rc1
References: FATE#326289 FATE#326079 FATE#326049 FATE#322398 FATE#326166

The virtual Exynos DRM device has no runtime PM enabled, so checking
for its runtime suspended state is useless.

